jQuery News Ticker
-----------------------------------
	 	
An easy to use, slick and flexible news ticker in the style of the BBC News page ticker (http://news.bbc.co.uk).
	 	
Recommended for jQuery 1.4.x only. Now compatible with jQuery 1.3.2!	 	

Please visit http://www.jquerynewsticker.com/ for full documentation and downloads (including minified versions).
	 	
